cpd-api-save-diagram-elements-update-com: Okumanyisibwa aha obumanyiso bwa ekishushani bwanyima ya okubiika ekishushani
cpd-api-save-diagram-elements-param-elem: JSON ekakora Kodi ey'obumanyiso bw'ebishushani obwiine ku geitwamu (ninga obutereezibwe bwaba buriho) omu Wiki. Buri kamanyiso nkatekwa ku kugira ebishumuruzo ebi; ''Title'' nana ''content'' biri kushushana  na title nana content eya wiki.
cpd-api-delete-orphaned-elements-param-e: JSON ekakora Kodi ey'obumanyiso bwa ebishushani ebyiine kuba nibi sangurwa aha Wiki, ahabwokuba bikiihwa omu kishushani. Buri kamanyiso akekishushani keine kuba keine omutwe mukuru oguri kushushana na Orubaju rwa Wiki.
cpd-api-delete-orphaned-elements-update-: Raamba akamanyiso nka akatiine buzaare nezindi kugirabakeiheho.
cpd-saving-error-elements-save: Yaremwa ku tekayo obumanyiso-bw'obushushani obwa wiki
apihelp-cpd-save-diagram-elements-summar: Nebiika obumanyiso bwa ekishushani Kya BPMN nka Embaju za wiki, ninga neburabyaho bwabwa buriho
apihelp-cpd-delete-orphaned-elements-sum: Nesangura obumanyiso bwa ekishushani Kya BPMN, obwabiire bwihirweho
